  <name>Vozes</name>
  <summary>Voice dictation using whisper.cpp</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Vozes is a simple voice dictation application that uses whisper.cpp for high-quality, 
      offline speech-to-text. It allows you to dictate text into any application 
      using a global hotkey or voice activation.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>High-quality offline transcription.</li>
      <li>Global hotkey support (default F12).</li>
      <li>Voice activation ("Hey Jarvis").</li>
      <li>Easy setup with guided assistant.</li>
      <li>Supports multiple languages.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
